    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** 9.3.58-1\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Yes\n**Reproducible in production?:** Yes\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:** https://test-management.browserstack.com/projects/2219752/test-runs/TR-17851/folder/13176908/73685192/1321448031\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):** applausetester+bm8902@applause.expensifail.com\n**Issue reported by:** Applause Internal Team\n**Bug source:** Regression TC Execution\n**Device used:** Web\n**App Component:** Other\n\n## Action Performed:\nPrecondition - \nQBO connection is established in the workspace.\n\n1. Go to https://staging.new.expensify.com\n2. Create a expense in the workspace \n3. Submit an expense\n4. Approve this expense\n5. Press More > Export > Export to QBO\n\n## Expected Result:\nprimary action should show the Export button instead of Pay button after the export fails\n\n## Actual Result:\nAfter clicking the Export to QBO button in More Options, the primary action button changes to Pay. then after the export fails, the primary action in the report does not revert to Export, although the primary action in the expense preview updates correctly to Export.\n\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n\n## Platforms:\n- [ ] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [ ] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] Windows: Chrome\n- [ ] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e1477aee-7f7a-4c39-bd3f-ed833249ce28\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @Krishna2323</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022042641099612060416</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2042641099612060416</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-04-10</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
