    "body": "## Problem\nThe search list currently keeps `BillingGracePeriodEnds` `useOnyx` subscriptions inside individual list items.\n\n## Proposal\nRaise the `BillingGracePeriodEnds` subscriptions out of the list items and pass the resolved values down from `SearchList` so rows subscribe less aggressively.\n\n## Context\nThis issue was created to track https://github.com/Expensify/App/pull/87625.\n\n## Why this helps\nThis is a performance-oriented refactor intended to reduce row-level subscriptions in FlashList and improve Search rendering time.\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @jmusial</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022042620360719647544</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2042620360719647544</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-04-10</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
